This is a 16-bit color graphic library for TFT displays based on following controllers: ili9341, ili9488, st7735 and st7796.
The library supports SPI or FSMC approaches to connect the display.
The library can work on STM32 micro-controllers and uses HAL development library.
Directory structure:
Inc & Src directories is the example source code that illustrate how to use the library.
FatFS is a generic FAT library (http://elm-chan.org/fsw/ff/00index_e.html) that has been configured to work with SD-card
SD_SPI is a driver for SD-card reader connected via SPI bus
TFT is a graphic library source directory

UPDATED Feb 04 2023
Added the touch screen library based on XPT2046 IC
